{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id142ff030-3a70-11f1-b089-c1e1e512a22d","identifier":"/us/usc/t21/s360bbb–1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"360bbb–1"},"text":"§ 360bbb–1.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Dispute resolution","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"If, regarding an obligation concerning drugs or devices under this Act or section 351 of the Public Health Service Act [","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s262"},"text":"42 U.S.C. 262","children":[],"tail":"], there is a scientific controversy between the Secretary and a person who is a sponsor, applicant, or manufacturer and no specific provision of the Act involved, including a regulation promulgated under such Act, provides a right of review of the matter in controversy, the Secretary shall, by regulation, establish a procedure under which such sponsor, applicant, or manufacturer may request a review of such controversy, including a review by an appropriate scientific advisory panel described in "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t21/s355/n"},"text":"section 355(n) of this title","children":[],"tail":" or an advisory committee described in "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t21/s360e/g/2/B"},"text":"section 360e(g)(2)(B) of this title","children":[],"tail":". Any such review shall take place in a timely manner. The Secretary shall promulgate such regulations within 1 year after "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1997-11-21"},"text":"November 21, 1997","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id142ff031-3a70-11f1-b089-c1e1e512a22d"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1938-06-25/ch675/s562"},"text":"June 25, 1938, ch. 675, § 562","children":[],"tail":", as added "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/105/115/tIV/s404"},"text":"Pub. L. 105–115, title IV, § 404","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1997-11-21"},"text":"Nov. 21, 1997","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/111/2368"},"text":"111 Stat. 2368","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id142ff032-3a70-11f1-b089-c1e1e512a22d"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id142ff033-3a70-11f1-b089-c1e1e512a22d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"id142ff034-3a70-11f1-b089-c1e1e512a22d"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"This Act, referred to in text, is the Federal Food, Drug, and Cosmetic Act, ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1938-06-25/ch675"},"text":"act June 25, 1938, ch. 675","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/52/1040"},"text":"52 Stat. 1040","children":[],"tail":", which is classified generally to this chapter. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t21/s301"},"text":"section 301 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"id142ff035-3a70-11f1-b089-c1e1e512a22d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"effectiveDate","id":"id142ff036-3a70-11f1-b089-c1e1e512a22d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Effective Date","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section effective 90 days after ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1997-11-21"},"text":"Nov. 21, 1997","children":[],"tail":", except as otherwise provided, see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/105/115/s501"},"text":"section 501 of Pub. L. 105–115","children":[],"tail":", set out as an Effective Date of 1997 Amendment note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t21/s321"},"text":"section 321 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
